{
  "stem": "11174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, maybe I didn't tell him that I have to give back the gold and the silver.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German, the officer, got very angry at him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, if you are [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you don't clear-- close your mouth, I'll shoot you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That guy got so-- yes, but he-- when the officer took-- he asked me the address where to write it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, if he meant it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Apparently it seems that the man did, because he wrote down my address.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He gave it to that [NON-ENGLISH] to see that it's done, let know the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "While he get it and he saw what was going to happen, he started to soften up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's when the officer got angry at him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he hollered don't shoot him, so he ran.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somehow he dropped that little slip with my name and address.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he had told him to help and to get it back and he ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The officer on the other side, the soldier that was standing there on guard, he told him to go on the other side and he called them out to shoot.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he says one, two, and three, or something, and he shot at me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All-- I was numb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "All I felt is like a freeze going through under my skin, you know, a freeze.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And under the skin of my head especially.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it's quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was sure I heard talk that if you get shot, you don't really feel pain right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I'm waiting to fall and I don't fall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Took-- it took only seconds probably.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But to me, it looked like who knows how long.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
